nce and the US delegation so bad he should just send them home to prove he has “all the cards” no respect = no negotiations.  SEND THEM HOME!\n\n#oott $xle $uso $es $vix", "time": "18:55", "author": "TheWuhanClan", "author_name": "Wuhan Fourth Turning Swan", "followers": 20042, "views": 418, "likes": 2, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2068772817861230968", "url": "https://x.com/CRUDEOIL231/status/2068772817861230968", "text": "As of 12 hours ago, two dirty tanker STS operations active in UAE Fujairah waters, alongside two clean tanker STS transfers running off Shinas, Oman.\n\n#oott #iran https://t.co/rjohiu8wQc", "time": "19:07", "author": "CRUDEOIL231", "author_name": "JH", "followers": 59314, "views": 24152, "likes": 136, "replies": 5, "retweets": 16, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2068799371261431844", "url": "https://x.com/TheWuhanClan/status/2068799371261431844", "text": "Bitcoin crashing as Iran talks collapse 🚩 #oott $es $spy $btc $mstr $eth $coin $sol $vix", "time": "20:53", "author": "TheWuhanClan", "author_name": "Wuhan Fourth Turning Swan", "followers": 20042, "views": 941, "likes": 2, "replies": 1, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2068826240337826172", "url": "https://x.com/rjplanetb/status/2068826240337826172", "text": "You guys are watching minute by minute. Im watching the macro picture. Watch the the CRUDE DRAWS this week. They are NOT stopping any time soon and there is a violent squeeze on oil incoming #OOTT", "time": "22:39", "author": "rjplanetb", "author_name": "George Orwell", "followers": 274, "